Carl-Hamm Pipes, Pumps and Solutions is taking the concept of open pit dewatering to a new level. Consider the benefits if dewatering without the cost required for in-pit dewatering infrastructure that requires heavy-duty maintenance and constant upkeep as pits deepen over time. This never-been-done before dewatering methodology is breaking pit dewatering boundaries. Pilot tested already, it is ready for market and will revolutionise the way you think about mining, without the timely distraction of constantly pumping water out the pit first. Watch the video to find out more about this exciting initiative.